er.com/6GkjbbYNPw</a></p>— BBC Woman's Hour (@BBCWomansHour) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BBCWomansHour/status/1390320448643031041?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 6, 2021</a></blockquote> \n\n\n\n<p>Finally, this month’s edition of <a href=\"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJwtkUtuxCAQRE8z7Mbi4w9esMgm17AwNB40GBC0E_n2wfFICKHuKlXpYTTClsqpcqpIrmvBM4OK8FsDIEIhR4WyeKv4yGfa85lY1VsmB0l8XVwB2LUPCssBJB9r8EajT_FyiIFLTl7KTIZxOzo6gpBcC2cnxh3T_SyckRruXH1YD9GAgh8oZ4pAgnoh5voQXw_-3Q6-wJwm-LjlZI2u2Jm0tzlkX5OFekueH83zI3o62H30kXjFKWd0oBMb2djLjnWOwio40Kk3MLVmnMLQugk5isnpdXj0dN94V4-1ojbvK48Updf17HZv3nA2wScOfa7XvtPHxWFpz_2IHs8Fol4D2BsR3qT_oS0bRCjtB-yiUbGR074BZvMw0BvJxXBkvZjkQFoHm5orql3vPhTIEAKUP6Q6mL0\">The </a><strong><a href=\"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJwtkUtuxCAQRE8z7Mbi4w9esMgm17AwNB40GBC0E_n2wfFICKHuKlXpYTTClsqpcqpIrmvBM4OK8FsDIEIhR4WyeKv4yGfa85lY1VsmB0l8XVwB2LUPCssBJB9r8EajT_FyiIFLTl7KTIZxOzo6gpBcC2cnxh3T_SyckRruXH1YD9GAgh8oZ4pAgnoh5voQXw_-3Q6-wJwm-LjlZI2u2Jm0tzlkX5OFekueH83zI3o62H30kXjFKWd0oBMb2djLjnWOwio40Kk3MLVmnMLQugk5isnpdXj0dN94V4-1ojbvK48Updf17HZv3nA2wScOfa7XvtPHxWFpz_2IHs8Fol4D2BsR3qT_oS0bRCjtB-yiUbGR074BZvMw0BvJxXBkvZjkQFoHm5orql3vPhTIEAKUP6Q6mL0\">Cycling Podcast Féminin</a></strong> came out this week featuring a segment ranking teams’ performances throughout the classics as well as interviews with Anna Shackley and Riejanne Markus — who has a <a href=\"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJwlkMluxCAMhp9mOEYsgZADh15666UvELE4UzoEIpaJ8vYljWTZlu1ftj-rKzxTPtWeSkWXW-q5g4pwlAC1QkatQF68U1TQGY90Rk6NjkgukS_LmgE27YOquQHamwne6upTvBSMU0nRj5JmWmeCAQuwXGgjZ2I1kUxMjnJp2b1XN-chWlDwhnymCCion1r38mAfD_rZ7TiO4UytNgODTVuvXLf18O3hV8cIXzq_WumFt3eQCvKKYkowxxMRRIxyIMOKwTAKeBotTFQzioFPhDIp2LRqwx8j3p50KM2Uqu3r2oOy0sacw-btC84-YE8bfHxWv5erP-h2fb70dGvR13OBqE0Ad0OpN9t_TMsTIuTO3C26KiIoHjtSMnOObwgXNUFGNkmO-g0udVVUm958yLBDCJD_ALcMkmQ\">YouTube channel,</a> who knew?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Shop front of the week</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlikely to become a regular segment. Courtesy of Bella Mackie on Insta:</p>\n\n\n\n<